{"tid":1759522,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"暫時停止一下有關新區議會建議，先關注其他更重要既事","createTime":"2019-11-27T16:48:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-27T17:27:06.000Z","uid":81236,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"7cfdd69515e871c61aa1e12df14bbc2dbcc27534","tid":1759522,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T16:48:56.000Z","msg":"知道好多香港人都對嚟緊新區議會有好大期望<br />\n<br />\n亦都有好多唔同嘅建議想比區議員實行<br />\n<br />\n但現階段其實有更加多具迫切性既事情要大家專注先<br />\n<br />\n特別係而家呢個打資訊戰嘅年代<br />\n<br />\n對家已經用唔同嘅手法分散我哋注意力<br />\n包括甜post、標題黨、中共/黑警變軟等等<br />\n<br />\n目的就係要我地放低警戒鬆懈<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實有好多手足喺唔同方面都攻堅緊要大家既支持<br />\n係呢個時候有更多post值得喺連登熱門出現<br />\n<br />\n有理大既手足被困仲未出黎要大家支援<br />\n有嚟緊幾日唔同既大遊行同埋集會需要人手文宣<br />\n有英國領事館手足留守要大家支持<br />\n有失蹤手足要大家關注<br />\n有馬鞍山手足突然俾捕<br />\n<br />\n太多太多<br />\n<br />\n希望大家唔好諗住成期做觀眾冷氣軍師<br />\n大家一齊落場行動做姪魔同埋衝鋒21啦<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/captvhk/videos/2683455038548946/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcaptvhk%2Fvideos%2F2683455038548946%2F&d=iBLSwy1tqwhlDNpwtuM9DSwbHaueoKb2XZOoGTcnCr8%3D&h=a0e46700\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/captvhk/videos/2683455038548946/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後有關區政建議，如果係地區性<br />\n<br />\n除左連登比意見外，希望黎緊大家可以親身去比意見同埋參與社區改善工程<br />\n<br />\n一）因為只有你最知道自己果區有咩要改善<br />\n二）好多既建議要實行既話係需要大家高度參與<br />\n<br />\n所以鼓勵大家黎緊有咩想反映/參與都可以去區議員辦事處"},{"pid":"561e7651880b47b016d0c5f00426cb32a9dae27a","tid":1759522,"uid":26190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T16:49:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ec21949fb065518a5025018c19d49b63df5e602b","tid":1759522,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T16:51:25.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"8cb13032d27e56d78a4ea6aa501ed1a564b10eda","tid":1759522,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T16:52:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3q6WEBn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3q6WEBn.jpg&h=026c7e19&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c51af323fead49565b0ef69b404f117cb68d780a","tid":1759522,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T17:12:34.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"93c8d9abe3ca284c49a45fac849183e4c0d18fe0","tid":1759522,"uid":231480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T17:13:27.000Z","msg":"係，理大係緊急情況"},{"pid":"38bb76255fdc80e34e37f220b6f6e721a307e695","tid":1759522,"uid":31952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T17:14:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"39aca8d0936a89768dfe1bf86f8002bd22ced912","tid":1759522,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T17:27:06.000Z","msg":"Push"}]}